Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.05,0:00:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘的移动要塞侵攻作战被阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.89,0:00:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球得以保全
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.43,0:00:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A.G 151年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 笑起来多像你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 像亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.69,0:00:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.56,0:00:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字叫吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.43,0:01:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真忍心扔下这可爱的孩子去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.24,0:01:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后一次任务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.48,0:01:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.45,0:01:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会有这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样善良的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不该上战场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想让他们生活在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有战争的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此 现在必须战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时光飞逝…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是勇气纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是漫长战争开始的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.43,0:02:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会见到父亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天国的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争还没有结束
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屈身于红色星球的战士们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们理想乡的实现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的计划即将 进入最终篇章
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘之旗 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飘扬在地球神圣大地的日子不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要大家的力量 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊泽尔坎特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温蒂 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广场上的机动战士展快要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到个绝佳的景点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去就上车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:04:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勒布鲁斯 考出驾照了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这车是问爸爸借的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 有个派对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好像是吉欧爷爷的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧最亲爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 哪里有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BIGRING防线内发现未知物体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,综合解析系统认为90%是维甘移动要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有发现这庞然大物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士部队紧急出动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时命令周边舰队…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在敌方移动要塞上 发现巨大热量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是高功率光束武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见了吗 德勒尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始的钟声 响起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这感觉 是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 你父亲的遗物？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛基没听说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧父亲的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸是联邦军机师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我出生后不久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一次调查漂流船的任务时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 别瞎说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后 军队前往调查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了这块AGE装置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 地球上也要打仗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人… 那就是维甘…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急召回 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知不当班的士官 会还他们假期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告机动战士队情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布兰克斯小队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经出击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯小队也即将出击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 什么勇气纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 这就出发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜路亚　乔纳森
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥迪克　德比克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:08:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时OK
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 什么情况？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令部不会把坏情况告诉前线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是听见了吧 皮特的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮特… 那个通讯员？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次听到皮特那种发颤的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他外遇被老婆发现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可见情况之危急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了 战场福尔摩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之这次不同往常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别大意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍利奇·阿比斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cnanche CUSTAM 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 情况不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会有事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我名为伊泽尔坎特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活在火星圈的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独立国家维甘的代表者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 地球种
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘在此宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式开始侵略地球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵略地球？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各军区报告出现维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅限于奥利巴诺兹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多的维甘 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直隐藏在地球上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居民们请迅速前往
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿伦特河的避难区
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 居民们请迅速前往阿伦特河…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停车 勒布鲁斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:10:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再耽搁我们自身难保
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我在这里下车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.63,0:11:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温蒂 你们先走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说我没劝过你们
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.96,0:11:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着三个孩子打算这么过来？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就去喊军人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕 一起过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去避难区吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去避难区
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们被落下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用您的车送他们走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平民去阿伦特河避难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.06,0:13:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没接到通知吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军对平民孩子见死不救？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上士 事态紧急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们快上来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温蒂 孩子拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事？ 不上车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也和吉欧一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你照顾好这些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达一定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷的高达是最强的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 上来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我们去哪儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去启动高达
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 救世主登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天该告诉我藏高达的地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机翼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:15:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力拉操纵杆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞起来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是核心战机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核心战机 那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.04,0:15:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候混进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好严重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥利巴诺兹被…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让天神号做好出发准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管那么多 快去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神号是爷爷以前搭乘的战舰？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然是艘老旧船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要有那艘船和高达
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥利巴诺兹就有救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达在那上面？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接驾驶核心战机靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跳上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西的驾驶就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人驾驶不了它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G-Scepter
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来会变形成高达是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是变形
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是合体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合体？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意听着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:17:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达是由G-Scepter和核心战机合体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组成一台机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上开始合体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是还在飞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事 电脑会负责细节操作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷…这也太突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.08,0:17:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 试试
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 把AGE装置插入右手插口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后打开30号到35号开关
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据屏幕指示拉动拉杆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了没
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后按下操纵杆上的G键
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就现在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.17,0:18:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是… 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达AGE-3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别松懈 好戏才刚开场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕吗 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 驱动高达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且 继承高达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来 驱动高达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了 可是怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达的操纵方式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你玩的模拟战一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是普通的游戏机？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷为了这一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束军刀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放跑它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是用天神号光子爆破炮技术
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研发的新武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西格玛希斯步枪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮击型
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏里打过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它载有大量弹药
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果成功引爆…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又进化了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后你就是高达的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:21:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.48,0:22:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.40,0:22:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.15,0:22:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又与我过不去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.13,0:22:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它从上面来了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.71,0:23:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战火笼罩的城市中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.93,0:24:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰船再次启航
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.79,0:24:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反击的闪光是否预示着未来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.51,0:24:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士高达AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.85,0:24:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争城市
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.65,0:24:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人的命运成就历史
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TVCM------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.62,0:24:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘耗时多年
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.48,0:24:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将刺客派往地球
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.41,0:24:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为一起掀起精心策划的突袭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.58,0:24:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球从内部瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.87,0:24:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夜之间
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.37,0:24:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再只属于地球联邦统治
